<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The DTV Visa Guide — Stay in Thailand Legally for Up to 5 Years</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold-deep: #B8860B;
            --gold-light: #D4AF37;
            --cream: #FDF8F3;
            --cream-dark: #F5EDE4;
            --green-soft: #6B8E6B;
            --green-dark: #4A6B4A;
            --charcoal: #2C2C2C;
            --charcoal-light: #3D3D3D;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--cream);
            color: var(--charcoal);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .brand-font {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: var(--white);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gold-deep);
        }

        .nav-cta {
            background: var(--gold-deep);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-cta:hover {
            background: var(--charcoal);
        }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream) 0%, var(--cream-dark) 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 0%, rgba(184,134,11,0.03) 100%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--gold-deep);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: var(--gold-deep);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.35rem);
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--gold-deep);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--charcoal);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--charcoal);
            border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .hero-trust {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
        }

        .hero-trust strong {
            color: var(--gold-deep);
        }

        /* Story Section */
        .story {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .story-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-label {
            color: var(--gold-deep);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .story h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
        }

        .story-content {
            display: grid;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .story-photo {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            background: var(--cream-dark);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .story-text p {
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
        }

        .story-text strong {
            color: var(--charcoal);
        }

        .story-highlights {
            background: var(--cream);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--gold-deep);
        }

        .story-highlights ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .story-highlights li {
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
        }

        .story-highlights li::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--green-soft);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Video Section */
        .video-section {
            padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--cream-dark);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .video-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .video-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 16/9;
            background: var(--charcoal);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Quiz Section */
        .quiz-section {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .quiz-container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .quiz-section h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .quiz-section > .quiz-container > p {
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .quiz-box {
            background: var(--cream);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            text-align: left;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px var(--shadow);
        }

        .quiz-progress {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .quiz-progress-bar {
            flex: 1;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--cream-dark);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .quiz-progress-bar.active {
            background: var(--gold-deep);
        }

        .quiz-question {
            display: none;
        }

        .quiz-question.active {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
        }

        .quiz-question h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--charcoal);
        }

        .quiz-options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .quiz-option {
            background: var(--white);
            border: 2px solid var(--cream-dark);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .quiz-option:hover {
            border-color: var(--gold-deep);
            background: var(--cream);
        }

        .quiz-option.selected {
            border-color: var(--gold-deep);
            background: rgba(184,134,11,0.05);
        }

        .quiz-result {
            display: none;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .quiz-result.show {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        .quiz-result-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .quiz-result h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .quiz-result p {
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .quiz-result .btn {
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        /* Products Section */
        .products {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--cream-dark);
        }

        .products-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .products h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .products > .products-container > p {
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow);
        }

        .product-card.featured {
            border-color: var(--gold-deep);
            position: relative;
        }

        .product-card.featured::before {
            content: 'Most Popular';
            position: absolute;
            top: -12px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--gold-deep);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .product-number {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: var(--cream);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gold-deep);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .product-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .product-card p {
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .product-price {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .product-price span {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .product-features {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .product-features li {
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            padding-left: 1.25rem;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
        }

        .product-features li::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--green-soft);
        }

        /* FAQ Section */
        .faq {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .faq-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .faq h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .faq-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-dark);
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .faq-question {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--charcoal);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .faq-question::after {
            content: '+';
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--gold-deep);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .faq-item.open .faq-question::after {
            content: '−';
        }

        .faq-answer {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
            color: var(--charcoal-light);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .faq-item.open .faq-answer {
            max-height: 500px;
            padding-top: 1rem;
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .cta-section {
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--charcoal);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-section p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .cta-section .btn-primary {
            background: var(--gold-deep);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
        }

        .cta-section .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--gold-light);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--charcoal-light);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--gold-light);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-container {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 5rem 1rem 3rem;
            }

            .quiz-box {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .product-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .story-highlights {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">The DTV Guide</div>
            <a href="#quiz" class="nav-cta">Check Eligibility</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-container">
            <div class="hero-badge">Thailand just ended the 60-day rule</div>
            <h1>Here's how to stay legally — <span>for up to 5 years</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">The exact system I used to get my DTV as a UK entrepreneur — formatted, structured, and ready for your application.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="#quiz" class="btn btn-primary">Take the Free Quiz</a>
                <a href="#products" class="btn btn-secondary">See the Guide</a>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-trust">
                <strong>5-year multiple entry visa</strong> · 180 days per stay · No more visa runs
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="story">
        <div class="story-container">
            <div class="section-label">My Story</div>
            <h2>I sold my house, left the UK, and made Thailand my base</h2>
            
            <div class="story-content">
                <div class="story-photo">
                    [Your Photo Here]
                </div>
                
                <div class="story-text">
                    <p>I'm a UK entrepreneur who <strong>sold up, put my house on the market, and relocated to Thailand.</strong> I still run my UK company remotely — and I'm now expanding into the Philippines.</p>
                    
                    <p>Thailand is my hub for Southeast Asia. And I hold a <strong>DTV visa</strong> — that's 5 years, multiple entry, 180 days per stay.</p>
                    
                    <p>With the 60-day rule now ending, the DTV is the best long-term option for most people. But embassy applications are strict — the £300 government fee is non-refundable — so getting it right matters.</p>
                    
                    <p>I spent <strong>10–15 hours</strong> preparing my application. Then I built an <strong>AI-assisted document formatting system</strong> that gets it done in a fraction of the time.</p>
                    
                    <p>This is NOT AI generating fake info. It formats <strong>YOUR</strong> real information correctly so embassies accept it.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="story-highlights">
                <ul>
                    <li>5-year DTV visa holder & UK entrepreneur</li>
                    <li>Remote company still running from Thailand</li>
                    <li>Built the exact system that got me approved</li>
                    <li>Helped others navigate the strict embassy requirements</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Video Section -->
    <section class="video-section">
        <div class="video-container">
            <div class="section-label">Watch</div>
            <h2>See how the DTV works in practice</h2>
            <div class="video-placeholder">
                [Video Embed Placeholder]
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Quiz Section -->
    <section class="quiz-section" id="quiz">
        <div class="quiz-container">
            <div class="section-label">Free Eligibility Check</div>
            <h2>Find out in 2 minutes if you qualify</h2>
            <p>Answer 7 quick questions. Get a personalised result.</p>
            
            <div class="quiz-box">
                <div class="quiz-progress">
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar active"></div>
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar"></div>
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar"></div>
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar"></div>
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar"></div>
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar"></div>
                    <div class="quiz-progress-bar"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 1: Remote Income -->
                <div class="quiz-question active" data-question="1">
                    <h3>Do you currently have remote income?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes-employed">Yes — I'm employed and work remotely</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes-self">Yes — I'm self-employed / run my own business</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes-freelance">Yes — I'm a freelancer with clients</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="no">No, I don't have remote income</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 2a: PAYE or Self-Employed -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="2a">
                    <h3>Are you PAYE (employed by a company) or self-employed?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="paye">PAYE — I'm employed by a company</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="self-employed">Self-employed / I run my own business</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 2b: Workplace Policy -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="2b">
                    <h3>Does your workplace have a policy that allows you to work abroad?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes">Yes, they allow remote work from abroad</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="no">No, they don't have a policy for this</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="unsure">I'm not sure / haven't checked</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 2c: Asked Permission -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="2c">
                    <h3>Have you asked your workplace for permission to work from Thailand?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes">Yes, and they're okay with it</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="asked-waiting">I've asked, waiting for response</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="no">No, I haven't asked yet</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 2d: Self-Employed Duration -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="2d">
                    <h3>How long have you been working for yourself?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="over-2-years">Over 2 years</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="1-2-years">1–2 years</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="6-12-months">6–12 months</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="under-6-months">Under 6 months</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 2e: Tax Return -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="2e">
                    <h3>Have you submitted a tax return for your self-employed income or business?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes-filed">Yes, I've filed at least one</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="not-yet-due">Not yet — business is new, not due yet</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="overdue">I should have but haven't</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="not-uk">Not UK-based / different tax system</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 3: Monthly Income -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="3">
                    <h3>How much do you typically pay yourself per month from your self-employed work or business?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="over-3k">£3,000+ / month</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="2-3k">£2,000–£3,000 / month</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="1-2k">£1,000–£2,000 / month</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="under-1k">Under £1,000 / month</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 4: Bank Balance -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="4">
                    <h3>Can you show 500,000 THB (approx. £11,000–£12,000 depending on exchange rate) in a bank account?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes-have">Yes, I have this already</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="yes-savings">Yes, but it's spread across accounts</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="soon">I'll have this in the next 3 months</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="no">No, this won't be possible</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Question 5: Employment Proof -->
                <div class="quiz-question" data-question="5">
                    <h3>Do you have documentation to prove your remote work status?</h3>
                    <div class="quiz-options">
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="contract">Employment contract stating remote work</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="letter">Employer letter confirming remote work</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="portfolio">Freelance portfolio + client contracts</div>
                        <div class="quiz-option" data-value="business-docs">Business registration / tax documents</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Result: No Remote Income -->
                <div class="quiz-result" id="result-no-remote">
                    <div class="quiz-result-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h3>The DTV Remote Work visa isn't right for you</h3>
                    <p>The DTV has a different category called <strong>DTV2 — Thai Soft Power</strong> that might work for you instead. This covers activities like:</p>
                    <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 1.5rem 0; color: var(--charcoal-light);">
                        <li>Muay Thai training</li>
                        <li>Thai cooking classes</li>
                        <li>Thai language courses</li>
                        <li>Medical treatment</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Same 5-year visa, same £300 fee — just a different purpose of visit.</p>
                    <a href="https://london.thaiembassy.org/en/page/destination-thailand-visa" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">See DTV2 Requirements</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Result: Need Workplace Permission -->
                <div class="quiz-result" id="result-need-permission">
                    <div class="quiz-result-icon">⏸️</div>
                    <h3>Stop here — you need workplace permission first</h3>
                    <p>The Thai Embassy requires an <strong>employment contract or certificate</strong> showing you're authorised to work remotely. If your workplace doesn't allow it, you can't get the DTV.</p>
                    <p><strong>Your next step:</strong> Ask your employer about their remote work policy. If they say yes, come back and continue this quiz.</p>
                    <p>If they say no, you might want to consider the <strong>DTV2 (Soft Power)</strong> route instead — cooking, Muay Thai, language courses, etc.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Result: Low Income Warning -->
                <div class="quiz-result" id="result-low-income">
                    <div class="quiz-result-icon">💡</div>
                    <h3>You may need additional income sources</h3>
                    <p>Under £1,000/month might be tight for Thailand living + the £11,000 bank requirement. The Embassy wants to see you can support yourself.</p>
                    <p>You're not disqualified — but consider:</p>
                    <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 1.5rem 0; color: var(--charcoal-light);">
                        <li>Building up additional income streams</li>
                        <li>Waiting until your business earns more</li>
                        <li>Looking at DTV2 Soft Power options instead</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Want to discuss your specific situation?</p>
                    <a href="#consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Result: Likely Qualify -->
                <div class="quiz-result" id="result-likely">
                    <div class="quiz-result-icon">✅</div>
                    <h3>You likely qualify for the DTV Remote Work visa</h3>
                    <p>Based on your answers, you're in a strong position to apply. You have remote income, the right documentation, and can meet the financial requirements.</p>
                    <p>Next step: Get your documents formatted correctly. The Thai Embassy is strict — the £300 fee is non-refundable, and missing or poorly formatted documents = delays or rejection.</p>
                    <a href="#products" class="btn btn-primary">See the Guide Options</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Result: Challenges -->
                <div class="quiz-result" id="result-challenges">
                    <div class="quiz-result-icon">⚠️</div>
                    <h3>You may face some challenges</h3>
                    <p>Not disqualifying, but worth addressing before applying. Common issues: bank balance timing, documentation format, or employment proof.</p>
                    <p>Book a consultation — I'll help you figure out the best path forward.</p>
                    <a href="#consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Book Free Call</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Products Section -->
    <section class="products" id="products">
